{"tid":874401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金毛賊劫7仔　扯高衫露電線 「1.5萬要WeChat Pay唔存錢會爆炸」","createTime":"2018-10-24T07:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T08:48:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6a41ded2f82a0014dcdaaf88a17ed972c263d492","tid":874401,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181024/20529272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F20529272&d=pHDFri3JC9cxyroEx5P5vARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4c6f2728\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F20529272&h=156c63a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181024/20529272</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月24日 <br />\n<br />\n金毛賊劫7仔　扯高衫露電線<br />\n「1.5萬要WeChat Pay唔存錢會爆炸」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181024/large/24la4p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F24la4p2.jpg&h=b2e15c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方圍封涉案便利店調查。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港發生一宗賊人企圖用WeChat Pay HK劫款奇案。一個金毛口罩男昨早衝入長沙灣一間7-Eleven便利店聲稱打劫，要求女店員為其WeChat Pay賬戶充值1.5萬元，其間一度掀開衣衫露出電線威嚇「有炸彈」，幸醒目女店員藉詞推卻「轉唔到」及按動警鐘，嚇退賊人。警方將案件列為企圖行劫，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進，正追緝涉案賊人下落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者：劉柏麟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場位於長沙灣保安道255號寶熙苑地舖7-Eleven便利店，昨早9時許，一個戴口罩金毛男子突然衝入便利店，以半鹹半淡廣東話大叫打劫，然後遞上手機及紙條，要求33歲姓黃女職員到收銀櫃枱為其手機WeChat Pay賬戶充值1.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店員稱「轉唔到」拒絕<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，賊人見女店員不為所動，一度拉高身上衣衫，露出纏有電線及黑盒的上半身，並聲稱「有炸彈」，企圖威逼女店員就範，惟他又無厘頭稱：「記得幫我報警，唔存（錢）的話10分鐘內爆！」店員見賊人神情有異，先以「轉唔到」為由推卻，然後不動聲色按警鐘，口罩男事敗奪門而逃，女店員待賊人遠遁後報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場圍封便利店外搜證並在附近兜截，但未有發現，其後向店員問話及翻查閉路電視錄影，在門外撿獲一個懷疑是賊人遺下的口罩，帶走化驗，案件列作企圖行劫，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊，正追緝一名年約30至40歲，中等身材，蓄啡金色短髮的男子，案發時身穿灰色長袖上衣和黑色短褲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181024/large/a0401a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181024%2Flarge%2Fa0401a.gif&h=033bcaca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金額超每日增值上限<br />\n<br />\n2016年12月起全港7-Eleven便利店提供WeChat Pay現金增值服務，一般用戶可透過綁定信用卡或進行身份認證作支付密碼設定，單次增值限額為5,000元，每日上限為1萬元，而未設置密碼的戶口每月只可增值500元，換言之賊人根本無法一次過增值1.5萬元至個人賬戶內。<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑表示，賊人不但無法一次過增值15,000元至WeChat Pay賬戶，且一旦便利店通知微信，賊人的賬戶很快便會被凍結，無法使用有關款項，形容對方是一名笨賊。<br />\n<br />\n賊人企圖以WeChat Pay轉賬劫款，本港已非首次，去年9月12日晚上，一名持雙程證來港的38歲內地廚師，在油麻地廟街兜搭一名鳳姐上樓進行性交易，未幾露出賊相，持開蠔刀指嚇及強姦鳳姐，<br />\n更拍下女方裸照，威逼交出總值1.5萬元財物，惟賊人未滿足，要求鳳姐利用WeChat Pay轉賬至其個人賬戶，最終未能成功，鳳姐不甘損失，待賊人鬆懈時逃離及大叫打劫，警員到場擒獲賊人，疑犯其後被判囚8年。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n實名制易查身份"},{"pid":"bab3f924954d3ab6295ec41e08ee71db6ef80a0a","tid":874401,"uid":36296,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"個「轉唔到」好有喜感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575a5c9a7ef7fb7ac465dfaa04df184c6330433f","tid":874401,"uid":193421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"其實個警鐘無聲會唔會無咁危險又易拉到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"dbe0e902b616af847fb37f9a951929bcd9e766f3","tid":874401,"uid":22450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:29:54.000Z","msg":"呢間7仔成日比人打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa75b0c886b057b78dbc2f2a81be1cf7c17b543","tid":874401,"uid":45120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:35:11.000Z","msg":"用得WE柒果然都係弱智居多"},{"pid":"e66e6bec42b9d842b182c5ee91c4fc2f6936c7fe","tid":874401,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/154055_72060f0b24588332c5e0f3e349b55942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F154055_72060f0b24588332c5e0f3e349b55942.jpg&h=1c79ccaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ngoogle中國usb有好多騙案"},{"pid":"09d00f639b2dad1488ed109b11983b18a6f45d65","tid":874401,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e66e6bec42b9d842b182c5ee91c4fc2f6936c7fe","tid":874401,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/154055_72060f0b24588332c5e0f3e349b55942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F154055_72060f0b24588332c5e0f3e349b55942.jpg&h=1c79ccaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ngoogle中國usb有好多騙案"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3487c530ae9225ce2780f587ee3cf57a22f6ac","tid":874401,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"露條賓周出黎好過啦"},{"pid":"e10f48efcc007198f97f5b0010b3d31fd3a015fa","tid":874401,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"死傻仔"},{"pid":"8092b8d9dde83af64e0c2ce1b0eaa56736e6a19d","tid":874401,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:48:59.000Z","msg":"條垃圾俾人笑足成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}